{"word":"σπαργανόω","slug":"σπαργανόω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>σπαργανόω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <el>σπάργᾰνον</el>\n<br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>like <a href='S:σπάργω'><el>σπάργω</el></a>\n<p/><i>to wrap in swaddling-clothes, swathe</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:participle'>part.</a> <el>ἐσπαργανωμένος</el> <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b><p/>"}]}